data.description: Come take a look at this home with a new great price! 3 bedroom 1.75 bath.  New siding and windows on the south side plus a double lot with space for a garden and a large deck for hanging out! Fresh paint inside!  2 car garage, Laminate wood floors, and so many windows to let the light in!  just a walk away to the Port of Peninsula and a 3 minute drive to Ocean Park for shopping, dining and more! This home is priced below assessed value so come and take a look before its too late!
